We get occasional false positives on our spam blacklist, which we need to identify the root cause of and fix.  This can be difficult when there is no obvious correlation to the content posted by the user and the contents of the blacklist.

When the blacklist finds a match, it should log the details of the specific match to the app log so that we can troubleshoot later on.

